ngDispatcher` instances\n\n**Validating Plugin**:\n- Extends the generic `Webhook` with the `newValidatingDispatcher()` factory\n- Provides the `newValidatingDispatcher()` function that creates `validatingDispatcher` instances\n\n### 7. Request Handling (pkg/admission/plugin/webhook/request/admissionreview.go)\n\nHandles conversion of admission requests to AdmissionReview format:\n- Creates `AdmissionReview` objects from admission attributes\n- Handles version negotiation between API server and webhooks\n- Manages response parsing and status extraction\n\n### 8. Matching and Predicates (pkg/admission/plugin/webhook/predicates/)\n\nMultiple matching stages filter which webhooks should be called:\n\n**rules/rules.go**:\n- `Matcher` evaluates if a request matches webhook rules\n- Checks API group, version, resource, operation, and scope\n- Supports wildcard matching\n\n**namespace/matcher.go**:\n- `Matcher` evaluates namespace selectors\n- Fetches namespace labels from the cluster lister\n- Applies label selector matching\n\n**object/matcher.go**:\n- `Matcher` evaluates object selectors\n- Checks labels on both old and new objects\n- Used for fine-grained filtering\n\n**matchconditions/matcher.go**:\n- CEL-based match condition evaluation\n- Compiles and executes CEL expressions\n- Supports access to admission request and authorizer context\n- Handles failure policies for evaluation errors\n\n### 9. API Type Definitions (kubernetes-api)\n\n**admissionregistration/v1/types.go**:\n- **`MutatingWebhookConfiguration`**: Top-level resource containing a list of `MutatingWebhook` objects\n- **`MutatingWebhook`**: Individual webhook configuration with name, client config, rules, failure policy, match policy, namespace/object selectors, side effects, timeout, admission review versions, and match conditions\n- **`ValidatingWebhookConfiguration`**: Top-level resource containing a list of `ValidatingWebhook` objects\n- **`ValidatingWebhook`**: Similar structure to `MutatingWebhook